
@startuml

' Define classes and their attributes

class Driver {
    - driverID: int (auto-generated)
    - name: String
    - isOnSickLeave: boolean
}

class Bus {
    - licensePlate: String (max 10 chars)
    - isInRepairShop: boolean
}

class Route {
    - routeNumber: int (max 9999)
}

class Assignment {
    - date: Date
    - bus: Bus
    - route: Route
}

class Shift {
    - shiftType: String (Morning, Afternoon, Night)
    - startTime: Time
    - endTime: Time
}

class DriverShiftAssignment {
    - date: Date
    - driver: Driver
    - shift: Shift
    - bus: Bus
    - route: Route
}

class Overview {
    - date: Date
    - route: Route
    - busesAssigned: List<Bus>
    - shifts: List<Shift>
    - driversAssigned: List<Driver>
}

' Relationships

Driver "1" -- "many" DriverShiftAssignment : assigned to
Bus "1" -- "many" Assignment : assigned to
Bus "1" -- "many" DriverShiftAssignment : served in
Route "1" -- "many" Assignment : has
Route "1" -- "many" Shift : has
Shift "1" -- "many" DriverShiftAssignment : covered by
DriverShiftAssignment "1" -- "1" Shift : uses
DriverShiftAssignment "1" -- "1" Driver : assigned
DriverShiftAssignment "1" -- "1" Bus : on
DriverShiftAssignment "1" -- "1" Route : for
Overview "1" -- "many" Route : includes
Overview "1" -- "many" Bus : shows
Overview "1" -- "many" Driver : shows
Overview "1" -- "many" Shift : includes

@enduml

---

### Explanation of Key Elements:

- **Driver**: Identified by a unique ID and name. Can be marked as on sick leave.
- **Bus**: Identified by a license plate (up to 10 characters). Can be marked as in repair.
- **Route**: Identified by a number (max 9999).
- **Assignment**: Links a **Bus** to a **Route** for a specific **Date**.
- **Shift**: Represents morning, afternoon, or night shifts with start/end times.
- **DriverShiftAssignment**: Associates a **Driver**, **Shift**, **Bus**, and **Route** for a particular **Date**.
- **Overview**: Provides a summary view for a given day, showing all relevant data including status flags.

---

